title: 28. The Last Dance: Developing Winning Tendencies Part 1
itunes:title: 28. The Last Dance: Developing Winning Tendencies Part 1
description: From Michael Jordan to Dr. Dre, Andy and the guys discuss segments from "The Last Dance" documentary, what it means to have the mentality of a winner, and the regression of hip hop music. Andy also dives deep into why it’s important to nurture a battle mindset and prove all those naysayers wrong.
